headline: T1 Energy Secures U.S. Solar Deals and Pushes $850 Million Texas Plant Forward
summary: T1 Energy signed a supply pact with Corning and a major U.S. utility while advancing its $850 million Texas solar cell plant amid rising domestic demand.
